                            The South Asian Liver Institute Hyderabad is our flagship center and the cornerstone of advanced liver care in South India. Located in the prestigious Banjara Hills area, our state-of-the-art facility has been serving patients since 2010 with world-class liver transplantation, hepatology services, and comprehensive care for all liver diseases.
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-block__desc mb-20">
                            Our Hyderabad center houses a dedicated liver transplant unit, advanced ICU with 24/7 critical care, modern operation theaters, comprehensive diagnostic facilities, and specialized hepatology clinics. We have performed over 2,000 successful liver transplants, making us one of the busiest liver transplant centers in India.
                        </p>
                        <h3 class="text-block__title mb-20">Services Offered at SALi Hyderabad</h3>
                        <ul class="list-items list-unstyled mb-40 pl-40">
                            <li><strong>Liver Transplantation:</strong> Living donor and deceased donor transplants with excellent outcomes</li>
                            <li><strong>Hepatology Services:</strong> Comprehensive medical management of all liver diseases</li>
                            <li><strong>Advanced Laparoscopic Surgery:</strong> Minimally invasive procedures for liver and biliary conditions</li>
                            <li><strong>Interventional Radiology:</strong> TACE, RFA, TIPS, and other image-guided procedures</li>
                            <li><strong>Therapeutic Endoscopy:</strong> ERCP, EUS, variceal banding, and advanced endoscopic procedures</li>
                            <li><strong>24/7 ICU Services:</strong> Specialized critical care for liver patients</li>
                            <li><strong>Diagnostic Services:</strong> Advanced imaging, FibroScan, laboratory testing</li>
                            <li><strong>Nutritional Counseling:</strong> Dedicated dietitians for liver disease management</li>
                        </ul>
                        <h3 class="text-block__title mb-20">Our Expert Team</h3>
                        <p class="text-block__desc mb-20">
                            SALi Hyderabad is staffed by a multidisciplinary team of liver transplant surgeons, hepatologists, anesthesiologists, intensivists, interventional radiologists, gastroenterologists, and specialized nursing staff. Our team includes nationally and internationally trained specialists with decades of combined experience in liver care.
                        </p>
                        <h3 class="text-block__title mb-20">Facility Highlights</h3>
                        <ul class="list-items list-unstyled mb-40 pl-40">
                            <li>Modular operation theaters with HEPA filtration</li>
                            <li>20-bed dedicated liver ICU</li>
                            <li>Advanced imaging: CT, MRI, ultrasound</li>
                            <li>Dedicated endoscopy suite</li>
                            <li>On-site blood bank and laboratory</li>
                            <li>Patient and family accommodation facilities</li>
                            <li>Pharmacy and ambulance services</li>
                        </ul>
                        <h3 class="text-block__title mb-20">Location & Accessibility</h3>
                        <p class="text-block__desc mb-20">
                            <strong>Address:</strong> Plot No. 8-2-269/4/B, 4th Floor, Road No. 2, Banjara Hills, Hyderabad, Telangana 500034
                        </p>
                        <p class="text-block__desc mb-20">
                            Our center is easily accessible from all parts of Hyderabad and neighboring states. We are located near major landmarks in Banjara Hills, with ample parking facilities. The Rajiv Gandhi International Airport is approximately 30 km away (45 minutes drive).
                        </p>
                        <h3 class="text-block__title mb-20">Patient Support Programs</h3>
                        <p class="text-block__desc mb-20">
                            We offer comprehensive patient support through our LICAP (Liver Cancer Awareness Program), Liver Line helpline, and Ascites Club for cirrhosis patients. Our social workers assist with insurance claims, financial counseling, and accommodation arrangements for out-of-town patients.
                        </p>
